I'm not getting any email on my computer pc.

The reason of not getting any email on the pc could be caused by a update or vpn service. Try to disconnect all these topics like antivirus , vpn , to check for mail after switching them on or off. Most regonised issues are after a update of Thunderbird , the previous program where trusted in the list of trusted software and the new installed software is not try to change this to erase the recent trusted version and put the new selected version on the list or wait after deleting it from the list of trusted programs list for the drop down box to follow.
